title: unicode-match-property-value-ecmascript [![unicode-match-property-value-ecmascript on npm](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/unicode-match-property-value-ecmascript)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/unicode-match-property-value-ecmascript)
description: unicode-match-property-value-ecmascript matches a given Unicode property value or property value alias to its canonical property value without applying loose matching, per the algorithm used for RegExp Unicode property escapes in ECMAScript. Consider it a strict alternative to loose matching.
